# 🃏 Pokerface  
**Version:** v2024.06.10  
**© 2004–2024 PretendGINEERS. All Rights Reserved.**

A networked, multi-client poker game written in **C**, featuring a **client–server architecture**, **socket programming**, **multithreading**, and a **GUI-based client**.

